  "instructions": [
    "Cook the penne rigate in a large saucepan of boiling salted water until al dente, about 8-10 minutes.",
    "Drain the penne rigate and return it to the saucepan.",
    "Add the cottage cheese, feta cheese, kalamata olives, and garlic to the saucepan with the penne rigate.",
    "Stir in the white wine vinegar and extra virgin olive oil.",
    "Season the mixture with salt, black pepper, and freshly chopped parsley.",
    "Transfer the penne rigate mixture to a large serving dish or individual plates.",
    "Sprinkle the crumbled goat gjetost cheese over the top of the penne rigate mixture.",
    "Dot the top of the goat gjetost cheese with black pepper.",
    "Garnish the dish with additional chopped scallions and parsley, if desired."
  ],
